          "reviewBody": "One of the best schools in Pune\nYou get admitted here after clearing 2 exams and one interview. The education board is CBSE. The teaching methods are exceptionally well and provides overall development of the students. If you take a review, students of every batch are admitted to IITs, MBBS, IISERs, PhD abroad and are doing well in their careers. The school promotes physical education, marketing skills, social skills equally.",
