            "ratingValue": "5",
            "bestRating": "5",
            "worstRating": "1"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have seen many reviews about Jnana Prabodhini school but not seen the correct information. Here I'm giving my review.\n\nJnana Prabodhini Prashala, is a high school located in sadashiv pune. It was started by educationist Dr. V. V. Pendse, in 1962.\n\nThe educational system is based development of the various mental and intellectual aspects of brain. The school entertains mainly the 'gifted' students. The students are selected through a two level entrance examination in which the Basic Mental Ability of a candidate is tested.\nMany cultural and social activities are taken place here . I have never seen such a best school ever .",
